---
name: "complexity-assessment-dialog"
version: "1.0.0"
layer: "extension"
description: "Dialog prompt asking the user to confirm or override complexity assessment"
params:
  - name: "issueNumber"
    type: "number"
    description: "Issue number being assessed"
    required: true
  - name: "issueTitle"
    type: "string"
    description: "Issue title for display"
    required: false
  - name: "assessedComplexity"
    type: "string"
    description: "AI-assessed complexity: XS, S, M, L, XL"
    required: true
  - name: "rationale"
    type: "string"
    description: "Brief rationale for the complexity assessment"
    required: false
---
Issue #{{issueNumber}}{{#if issueTitle}}: {{issueTitle}}{{/if}}

Assessed complexity: **{{assessedComplexity}}**
{{#if rationale}}
Rationale: {{rationale}}
{{/if}}

Confirm or override the complexity assessment to proceed with pipeline execution.
